com.samsung.android.sdk.composer.document

Class SpenContentDrawing

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.samsung.android.sdk.composer.document.SpenContentBase
      • com.samsung.android.sdk.composer.document.SpenContentDrawing

  • public class SpenContentDrawing
extends SpenContentBase
    SpenContentDrawing Class.
    ContentDrawing has the basic content properties by inherit the SpenContentBase,
    and has additional functions for drawing contents.
    Some APIs and variables are moved or integrated to super class SpenContentBase since 5.0.0.
    Since:
    5.0.0
